<topic id='attribute_source_of_admission.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: SOURCE OF ADMISSION - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The source of admission to a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_hospital_provider_spell">Hospital Provider Spell</xref>
 or a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_nursing_episode">Nursing Episode</xref>
 when the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 is in a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_hospital_site">Hospital Site</xref>
 or a 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_care_home">Care Home</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
National Code 51 
              <i>'NHS other hospital provider - 
                  <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_ward">WARD</xref>
 for general 
                  <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENTS</xref>
 or the younger physically disabled or A &amp; E department'</i>
 should not be used if the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 arrives at an 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_accident_and_emergency_department">Accident and Emergency Department</xref>
 and is admitted to the same 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_hospital_provider">Hospital Provider</xref>.        </p>
      <p>Notes:</p>
      <ul>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
The following National Codes have been introduced for the 
                                <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_mental_health_services_data_set">Mental Health Services Data Set</xref>
 
                                <b>only</b>
 to add further granularity to National Code 39 
                                <i>'Penal establishment,</i>
                  <i>
                     <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_court">Court</xref>
                  </i>
                  <i>, or Police Station /</i>
                  <i>
                     <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                           keyref="business_definition_police_custody_suite">Police Custody Suite</xref>
                  </i>
                  <i>'.</i>
 However, National Code 39 is still valid for the 
                                <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_mental_health_services_data_set">Mental Health Services Data Set</xref>
 where extra detail cannot be collected:                    </p>
            </div>
            <ul>
               <li>
                  <div>
                     <p>
40 
                                            <i>'Penal establishment'</i>
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <div>
                     <p>
41 
                                            <i>'<xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_court">Court</xref>'</i>
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <div>
                     <p>
42 
                                            <i>'Police Station / 
                                                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                                 keyref="business_definition_police_custody_suite">Police Custody Suite</xref>'</i>
                     </p>
                  </div>
               </li>
            </ul>
         </li>
         <li>
            <div>
               <p>
National Code 79 
                                <i>'Babies born in or on the way to hospital'</i>
 is 
                                <b>not</b>
 valid for the 
                                <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_mental_health_services_data_set">Mental Health Services Data Set</xref>.                    </p>
            </div>
         </li>
      </ul>
  </div>
</body>
